  "instructions": [
    "Heat the peanut oil in a wok over medium heat.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger, sauté for 30 seconds until fragrant.",
    "Add the sliced bell pepper, zucchini, and carrot, stir-fry for 4 minutes.",
    "Add the scallions and toasted peanuts, cook for another 2 minutes.",
    "Whisk honey, lime juice, soy sauce, chili flakes, and salt until well combined.",
    "Pour the glaze over the vegetables and peanuts, toss to coat.",
